  "title": "SALON OPERATION DIRECTOR",
  "description": "<p></p><ul><li>Incharge of the overall management and profitability of the salon.</li><li>Evaluate outlet operations and establish action plans for continuous improvement.</li><li>Perform advanced hair cutting and hair coloring such as highlights, ombre, and balayage.</li><li>Styles hair, including blowouts, curls, braids, ponytails, and updos.</li><li>Train and develop staff into service professionals and groom high potential into leadership roles</li><li>Curate marketing promotions to attract and retain new and existing customers.</li><li>Conduct monthy skillset trainings</li><li>Develops ongoing relationships with clients</li><li>Upsells clients on products and services</li><li>Developing and implementing sales processes for all staffs</li><li>Researching and analyzing data to create sales forecasts</li></ul><p>Requirements</p><ul><li>Atleast 15 years of relevant experience (salon base) at management level.</li><li>Results driven and customer-oriented</li><li>Good leadership skills</li><li>Good communication and customer service skills</li><li>Passionate creative about hair, beauty and fashion</li><li>Innovative and Energetic Workplace with a Growth Mindset</li></ul>",
